#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:895
#, no-c-format
msgid "In &yast;, click <menuchoice> <guimenu>Network Services</guimenu> <guimenu>Create New Directory Server</guimenu> </menuchoice> . Alternatively, start the module from command line with <command>yast2 ldap-server</command> ."
