msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "The instance name <emphasis>cannot</emphasis> be changed after the instance has been created. If you plan for only one LDAP server, use the default instance name <literal>localhost</literal> . However, if you plan to host multiple LDAP servers, use meaningful names for the individual instances."
