#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:927
#, no-c-format
msgid "In <guimenu>Directory suffix</guimenu> , enter the base domain name of the LDAP tree. It is your domain name split by component. For example, <literal>example.com</literal> becomes <literal>dc=example,dc=com</literal> ."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:934
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the mandatory security options, enter the password for the directory manager (LDAP's root/admin account) and repeat the password in the next step. The password must be at least 8 characters long."
