#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:941
#, no-c-format
msgid "To run &ds389; with a CA certificate, specify both of the following options:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:946
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the path to the <guimenu>Server TLS certificate authority in PEM format</guimenu> , with which the server certificates have been signed. <remark>taroth 2020-01-22: string may be simplified in the future, see https://github.com/yast/yast-auth-server/issues/55</remark>"
