#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:1160
#, no-c-format
msgid "--&gt; <!-- wbrown 2019-02-25: URLs or hostnames only. IP address would break TLS cn/san checking. --> Specify one or more LDAP server URLs or host names under <guimenu>Enter LDAP server locations</guimenu> . For security reasons, we recommend to use <literal>LDAPS://</literal> URLs only. When specifying multiple addresses, separate them with spaces."
