#. Tag: para
#: security_ldap.xml:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the appropriate LDAP distinguished name (DN) under <guimenu>DN of Search Base</guimenu> . For example, a valid entry could be <literal>dc=example,dc=com</literal> ."
